{"tid":50310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【燃燒140屋】日本新潟中華料理店起火 火勢迅速蔓延","createTime":"2016-12-22T10:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T12:35:04.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2e69c2fa202ecd8e847b95aec55cb29a45d5856","tid":50310,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"日本新潟縣一個臨海小城市發生火警，受大風影響火勢迅速蔓延，至少140幢建築物受波及，目前兩人受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n位於新潟縣的糸魚川市一間名為「上海軒」的中華料理店，周四早上首先起火，直至下午火勢已波及140間房屋，大火仍未救熄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nhfcw2so\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnhfcw2so&h=f8239173&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb3d6ba5d72aeda6b6f3ec574c0f1291edaec40","tid":50310,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e2ff42ea1b18dfdbc5c4760f8f6b8f7a4cd2bb","tid":50310,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4788c07adc9bd9bcf476760cf6f13d015033d93","tid":50310,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"睇圖仲以為山火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4d486686029edb4b12f29e294de9de6f76f63f","tid":50310,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:19:32.000Z","msg":"煉獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4ece58a243dc1fa83b750b278e90c26fce7cf3","tid":50310,"uid":57712